flowchart LR
    U([User]) -->|Upload docs| API[FastAPI Service]
    U -->|Ask question| API

    subgraph Ingestion
        ING[Loaders + Token-aware Chunker]
    end

    subgraph Retrieval & Generation
        RET[Hybrid Retriever<br/>BM25 + Vector RRF + Rerank]
        RAG[RAG Orchestrator<br/>LangChain grounded prompt]
    end

    API -->|parse + chunk| ING
    ING -->|embed| EMB[Embeddings Provider<br/>sentence-transformers / OpenAI]
    EMB --> VDB[(Vector Store<br/>FAISS)]
    API -->|retrieve top-k| RET
    RET --> VDB
    RET -->|context chunks| RAG
    RAG -->|grounded prompt| LLM[LLM Provider<br/>Ollama / OpenAI]
    LLM -->|streamed answer + citations| API
    API --> U
    API -. metrics .-> OBS[[Prometheus + Grafana]]
